          <li>
            <strong>
              Create a calendar
            </strong>
             - Get a unique 8-character ID and 6-digit PIN instantly
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>
              Share with friends
            </strong>
             - Send them the credentials (one message!)
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>
              Everyone marks their availability
            </strong>
             - Just click and drag
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>
              Find overlaps instantly
            </strong>
